						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying in the miṭṭa-chēnu to the east of the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in cyclic year <hi rend="bold"><hi rend="italic">Prabhava, Jyēshṭha,</hi> śu. 3.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the erection of a pillar by Prōlēju, son of Kāśī-Bōgōju, probably on behalf of certain individual Yiruga Mahārāju. In characters of the 14th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
